sure
all your country
has de itch; and keep
scratching
and
scratching
, as if de ware in hell, and could
get
brimstone
for noting; you
son
o'd a
whore.
The youke!
said
Duncan. Do you
impeach
me wi' the youke?
You impatche
yourself
,
said
