opinion
;
for it is a
necessary
, and ought to
be held a
sacred
, duty.
I dinna ken how it is,
said
Duncan;
but I
see
they hae every thing tail
foremost
in this kintry, to what they hae in
Scotland
:
a gauger a gentleman; and
weavers
in the
legislature
.
Just
at this
